Doors in dreams symbolize opportunities, choices, transitions, and emotional boundaries. They represent the thresholds you are approaching in your waking life.

An open door suggests new possibilities, growth, and readiness. You may be entering a new phase or embracing a fresh opportunity.

A closed door symbolizes obstacles, hesitation, or uncertainty. You may feel blocked or unsure about your next step. If the door is locked, it may reflect frustration or feeling shut out emotionally or professionally.

Walking through a door represents transition. You may be moving from one chapter of life to another—emotionally, spiritually, or practically.

A revolving door symbolizes cycles or repetitive patterns. You may feel stuck in a loop or unsure how to break free.

Doors are powerful dream symbols because they show you what is opening, what is closing, and what choices lie ahead.
